(52, 'st651n', 'hello my name is Eva.  I met melanie when I lost my son jake at 34 weeks, I then got pregnant again and lost my son Lucas at 32 weeks.  I have a five year old son, and I dont know if i can have any more children. I am so sorry for your loss also. I would love to join this site, but dont know how. Melanie mentioned that we have similar situations, and I feel not many people have gone through this twice. Thinking of you! and hope to be a part of this site soon. \r\nEva', 11, 6, '2010-06-11 17:42:37'),
