(19, 1, '2010-04-07 18:06:25', '2010-04-07 18:06:25', '</br>\r\n<div>Welcome………………………………………………………………………………………………………….</div>\r\n</br>\r\nThank you for stopping by hopeinloss.org, we hope you find your visit helpful and healing. Why we’re here…To provide a safe, secure, ad free, cost free, string free, online environment for parents dealing with the loss of a child late in pregnancy, or immediately after birth, so they may engage each other in a helpful and healing dialogue, that may otherwise be missing in their lives.\r\n\r\nAs parents — faced by this debilitating situation, twice, I can tell you — a service such as this would have helped  Susan and I immeasurably; in fact, we intend to use this site on a daily basis as we continue to struggle with the confusion and heartbreak of losing Will and Tiger.\r\n\r\nThe journey through this grief is one we’ll be on for the rest of our lives. Speaking of duration, access to this online tool will be extended to its members for life. Please stay tuned as we work to define our programs and update this site.\r\n\r\nWe expect a formal site launch in the coming months.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1-revision-14', '', '', '2010-04-07 18:06:25', '2010-04-07 18:06:25', '', 1, 'http://hopeinloss.org/2010/04/07/1-revision-14/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
