t nothing to lose in that. The emotion, the shared space, the loss of dreams.', 'grief expanded and compressed..... and expanded', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '123-revision-2', '', '', '2010-11-30 22:11:41', '2010-11-30 22:11:41', '', 123, 'http://susantomwillandtiger.hopeinloss.org/2010/11/30/123-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
